{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">From the very beginning, we carefully read all the ideas of our wonderful community. After analyzing your expectations, we decided to include in the first DLC for Farmer's Life those &quot;wishes&quot; that appeared most often and which we considered the most interesting.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\ud83c\udfda\ufe0f<strong>FARMER'S LIFE CONTENT - PIMP MY COTTAGE DLC</strong>\ud83c\udfda\ufe0f</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Possibility to throw everything out of the house except the door. We can also chop everything with an ax or cut it into boards with a saw.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">We can conveniently rearrange furniture and decorations, as well as pack them into parcels and sell them.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">We can sit on chairs, benches and stools.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The priest sells furniture, Stefan sells curtains, paints, wallpapers and floors, Ambro\u017cy sells trinkets (tablecloths, carpets, vases, clocks, thermometers, etc.)<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">\ud83c\udfd8\ufe0f<strong>New concrete and block buildings</strong>\ud83c\udfd8\ufe0f</h2></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">From now on, we can build large structures, almost straight from House Builder, which can be painted and the interior can be arranged however we want (including arranging positions as in wooden shelters)<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">\ud83d\udc36<strong>Cats and dogs</strong>\ud83d\ude3c</h2></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Finally, our little piggy Burek will have companions. Cats and dogs appear on the farm!</p></li></ul>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2926840/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1732235893","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2926840/page.bg.jpg?t=1732